# Tailwind CSS 4

This project uses Tailwind CSS 4 with the new CSS-first configuration.

## Configuration in `globals.css`

- `@import 'tailwindcss'` — no `tailwind.config.js`
- `@theme { }` — design tokens (colors, fonts, breakpoints, cursors)
- `@layer base { }` — font-face, global resets, focus styles
- `@layer components { }` — scoped component styles (.nav, .cases, etc.)
- `@utility name { }` — custom utilities (container-md, container-lg, link)

## Design Tokens

Semantic colors reference Tailwind palettes via CSS variables:

```css
--color-primary: var(--color-blue-50);
--color-black: var(--color-black-50);
--color-gray: var(--color-gray-50);
```

Custom breakpoint: `--breakpoint-xs: 340px`

## Patterns

- Use `@apply` for grouping Tailwind classes inside component layers
- Media queries use `@media (width > --theme(--breakpoint-md))` syntax
- Dark mode via `dark:` variant and `prefers-color-scheme`
- Container queries with `@3xl/cases:` syntax for responsive components
- Transitions always specify the property list explicitly
